725448f-a.title: Queens: 54th Avenue - 58th Street
725448f-a.text:
Fifty-fourth Ave. (Newtown Ave.), at the N.E. corner of 58th
Street, showing the original Betts homesteederected by Captain
Richard Betts about 1656 in Newtown. The site upon which it stood
is now a part of Mt. 2ion Cemetery.
Arthur White.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
